cff-version: 1.2.0
title: Hybrid quantum-classical RUL prediction for rolling bearings (XJTU-SY)
message: >-
  If you use this software, please cite it using the metadata from this file
  or the BibTeX block in README.md.
type: software
license: MIT
repository-code: "https://github.com/LisanHub/hybrid-qml-rul-bearing"
authors:
  - family-names: Lisan
    given-names: Zadid Al
