abstract: >-
  Pipeline for remaining useful life (RUL) estimation on XJTU-SY bearing data
  using an LSTM baseline and a hybrid variational quantum circuit model
  (PennyLane + PyTorch).
keywords:
  - remaining useful life
  - bearings
  - quantum machine learning
  - LSTM
  - PennyLane
  - XJTU-SY
